{"tid":2117812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"數據唔呃人　馬古尼防守勁過雲迪積克","createTime":"2020-07-21T05:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:38.000Z","uid":8968,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"803e25d066b4785c2136ac94b4efc7061152a83a","tid":2117812,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200717/mobile/bkn-20200717180038059-0717_00882_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20200717%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200717180038059-0717_00882_001.html%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D2&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=24d1fe21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200717/mobile/bkn-20200717180038059-0717_00882_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華基爾雲迪積克被公認為世界上最好的後衛之一，不過在上個夏天以破後衞世界紀錄8,500萬鎊，加盟曼聯的哈利馬古尼卻擁有更好的防守數據，一眾質疑馬古尼的球迷可能要大跌眼鏡！<br />\n<br />\n馬古尼整季表現經常受到批評，不過雲迪積克在周三對阿仙奴的比賽中，亦因一次回傳失誤間接令球隊輸波，所以賽後英國《太陽報》就趁勢比較一下兩位在今季的數據。<br />\n雲迪積克今季上陣時間和馬古尼差不多，基本上都是場場踢足。不過雲迪積克卻斬獲4個入球和1個助攻，比起馬古尼的1入球1助攻優勝。另外雲迪積克在傳球成功次數和成功率分別有2,735次和89.18%，亦比馬古尼的2,006次和86.43%高。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，馬古尼其他數據都是較佳的一方。首先雲迪積克有一個直接引致入球的大失誤，而在鏟球和鏟球成功率方面，馬古尼的35次和60%比雲迪積克的23次和52.17%為高；馬古尼在封阻方面亦有18次，多雲迪積克4次；67次攔截更比雲迪積克的39次多出一大截。兩位高大中堅頂上功夫同樣出色，不過馬古尼的92次頭槌解圍次數，亦勝過雲迪積克的80次。<br />\n<br />\n馬古尼雖然後上入球和傳送能力比雲迪積克弱，不過在防守數據上完全不失禮，曼聯只要給馬古尼配搭一位速度、轉身較快的中堅，後防線仍然可以信賴！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ynXRk9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ynXRk9.png&h=5d738328&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bf4bc65d99fc7126888aa5614b46bce84a74a86","tid":2117812,"uid":8968,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/afcmatthew/status/1284925558745452549?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fafcmatthew%2Fstatus%2F1284925558745452549%3Fs%3D21&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fcd6a9ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fafcmatthew%2Fstatus%2F1284925558745452549%3Fs%3D21&h=2d6a81cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/afcmatthew/status/1284925558745452549?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"8b9f91eff3963b35bea462fccdbcce861db6ed29","tid":2117812,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"新mustafi"},{"pid":"77ae0fae05f729fdf2c6837f1ec4e1b6f69285dd","tid":2117812,"uid":46587,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/ac-table-mustafi-vs-van-dijk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fac-table-mustafi-vs-van-dijk.jpg&h=75fd371f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"759b20393ec04e466ba7b41f39ebbe0745028906","tid":2117812,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"冰人屌打二人"},{"pid":"40fbcbc3c274d5b17dc74708c9249e27474cac9f","tid":2117812,"uid":191811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野馬古尼"},{"pid":"da86dac80ab01075fefa8c8adeeff9cfe3b78f6d","tid":2117812,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759b20393ec04e466ba7b41f39ebbe0745028906","tid":2117812,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"冰人屌打二人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"有個大牛龜拍檔好苦"},{"pid":"06df6e44422427b48a7eb51455ce85c5a93d94f7","tid":2117812,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"新連迪洛夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840132c2eeb9b9642253765f37a732be5a6ef31b","tid":2117812,"uid":138762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:00:37.000